=Wolfram Eberhard (1909-1989)=
==Publications==
===Monographs===
* Das Toba-Reich Nordchinas : Eine soziologische Untersuchung. Leiden: Brill, 1949
* Chinese Festivals. New York: Henry Schuman, 1952
* A history of China. Berkeley and Los Angeles: University of California Press, 1969.  (Revised and Enlarged Online Edition, 2006: [[@http://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/17695|Link]]).


